*! _fcoint_cv_fadl_single.ado -- FADL single frequency critical values
*! Banerjee et al. (2017) Tables 1a, 1b
program define _fcoint_cv_fadl_single, rclass
  syntax, n(integer) k(integer) tobs(integer) model(string)
  if `n' < 1 local n = 1
  if `n' > 3 local n = 3
  if `k' < 1 local k = 1
  if `k' > 5 local k = 5
